## ğŸ§© Architecture

1. User uploads a file
2. System scans content using regex patterns
3. PII is detected and validated
4. De-identification techniques are applied
5. Masked preview is generated
6. User downloads masked file and report

## ğŸŒŸ Novelty of the Project

* **Multi-Format Support:** Works with text, CSV, and PDF files
